                ],
                "logic": "and",
                "title": "Check you're eligible"
              },
              {
                "contents": [
                  {
                    "text": "Trustees are responsible for the operation of your charity. They must show they understand their legal requirements. ",
                    "type": "paragraph"
                  },
                  {
                    "contents": [
                      {
                        "href": "/guidance/trustee-board-people-and-skills",
                        "text": "Check who's eligible to be a trustee and what skills they need to have"
