                        "text": "Find and appoint trustees"
                      },
                      {
                        "href": "/government/publications/the-essential-trustee-what-you-need-to-know-cc3",
                        "text": "Read about your trustees' legal responsibilities"
                      }
                    ],
                    "type": "list"
                  }
                ],
                "title": "Find trustees"
              },
              {
                "contents": [
                  {
                    "contents": [
                      {
                        "href": "/guidance/charity-types-how-to-choose-a-structure",
                        "text": "Choose the right charity structure"
                      }
                    ],
                    "type": "list"
                  }
                ],
                "title": "Find out how to choose a charity structure"
              },
              {
                "contents": [
                  {
                    "text": "There are rules on what words you can use in your name.",
                    "type": "paragraph"
                  },
                  {
                    "contents": [
                      {
                        "href": "/setting-up-charity/name-your-charity",
                        "text": "Check what you can call your charity"
                      }
                    ],
                    "type": "list"
                  },
                  {
                    "text": "You cannot register a name that's the same as or similar to another charity.",
                    "type": "paragraph"
                  },
                  {
                    "contents": [
                      {
                        "href": "/find-charity-information",
                        "text": "Check the names of registered charities"
                      }
                    ],
                    "type": "list"
                  }
                ],
                "logic": "and",
                "title": "Choose a name for your charity"
              },
              {
                "contents": [
                  {
                    "text": "Your ‘purposes’ describe what your charity is set up to achieve.",
                    "type": "paragraph"
                  },
                  {
                    "contents": [
                      {
                        "href": "/guidance/how-to-write-charitable-purposes",
                        "text": "Find out how to write your charity's purposes"
                      }
                    ],
                    "type": "list"
                  }
                ],
                "logic": "and",
                "title": "Decide and write your charity's purposes"
              },
              {
                "contents": [
                  {
                    "text": "The governing document is a set of rules that explains how your charity is run. It needs to include your charity's structure, name and purposes. ",
                    "type": "paragraph"
                  },
                  {
                    "contents": [
                      {
                        "href": "/guidance/how-to-write-your-charitys-governing-document",
                        "text": "Find out how to write your governing document"
                      }
                    ],
                    "type": "list"
                  }
                ],
                "title": "Create a governing document"
              },
              {
                "contents": [
                  {
                    "text": "Your organisation must be able to show that it benefits the public. ",
                    "type": "paragraph"
                  },
                  {
                    "contents": [
                      {
                        "href": "/guidance/public-benefit-rules-for-charities",
                        "text": "Check how your organisation must benefit the public"
                      }
                    ],
                    "type": "list"
                  }
                ],
                "title": "Make sure you meet the 'public benefit requirement'"
              },
              {
                "contents": [
                  {
                    "text": "You must apply to register your charity with the Charity Commission if either:",
                    "type": "paragraph"
                  },
                  {
                    "contents": [
                      {
                        "text": "its income will be at least £5,000 per year"
                      },
                      {
                        "text": "it’s a charitable incorporated organisation (CIO)"
                      }
                    ],
                    "style": "choice",
                    "type": "list"
                  },
                  {
                    "contents": [
                      {
                        "href": "/setting-up-charity/register-your-charity",
                        "text": "Register with the Charity Commission"
                      }
                    ],
                    "type": "list"
                  },
                  {
                    "text": "You can register your charity’s details with HM Revenue and Customs (HMRC) to get tax back on things like Gift Aid donations.",
                    "type": "paragraph"
                  },
                  {
                    "contents": [
                      {
                        "href": "/charity-recognition-hmrc",
                        "text": "Register with HMRC"
                      }
                    ],
                    "type": "list"
                  }
                ],
                "title": "Register your charity"
              }
            ],
